== Definition ==

*A cultist is a member of a cult.[http://www.hyperdictionary.com/search.aspx?define=cultist]which is typically a small [[religion]] or a variation of another religion.

*An example of a cult would be [[Heaven's Gate]] and [[Peoples Temple]] as they are listed in the article Cult.

